main event: A farmer in Clearmont, Iowa, observed a circular object changing colors from red to green for 15 minutes on September 2, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed moving from south to north,The sighting occurred during dusk,No sound was heard during the sighting,The object was about the size of a quarter held at arm's length,The conclusion of the report was that the object was identified as a satellite (ECHO II).
